  <brief_title>Topotecan in Treating Patients With Myelodysplastic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase II Trial of Oral Topotecan Given Twice a Day for 5 Days or Once a Day for 10 Days to Patients With Myelodysplastic Syndromes (MDS)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
